{#- Compact "back to listing" link shown above the h1 on a note/project page,
    in place of the page icon (h1-icon.njk). It reserves the same vertical space
    as .h1-icon so the page title lines up with the listing page's title.
    Set `backUrl` and `backLabel` before including. -#}
<a class="back-link" href="{{ backUrl }}">{% phosphor "arrow-left", 16 %}<span>{{ backLabel }}</span></a>
